799
00:53:04,916 --> 00:53:06,199
You can talk to me now,

800
00:53:06,200 --> 00:53:07,483
or I can have you
officially deposed;

801
00:53:07,485 --> 00:53:09,351
We'll do it
at the police station.

802
00:53:09,353 --> 00:53:13,222
