803
00:53:13,224 --> 00:53:14,356
Marshalltown cops?

804
00:53:14,358 --> 00:53:16,225
No, Columbo.

805
00:53:16,227 --> 00:53:18,627
Eric, just a couple of minutes?

806
00:53:18,629 --> 00:53:20,262
Please.

807
00:53:21,465 --> 00:53:23,905
All right, fine. Back here.

808
00:53:27,638 --> 00:53:31,740
So all they told me
is that he was arrested drunk

809
00:53:31,742 --> 00:53:34,443
