to see you, right?

813
00:53:46,657 --> 00:53:48,257
I mean, that's why he was here.

814
00:53:48,259 --> 00:53:50,793
He came here first.

815
00:53:50,795 --> 00:53:52,728
How do you know that?

816
00:53:52,729 --> 00:53:54,662
Well, 'cause I talked to the
