room, I'll tell you that.

838
00:55:10,775 --> 00:55:12,841
When he died,

839
00:55:14,812 --> 00:55:18,447
I couldn't go to the funeral.

840
00:55:18,449 --> 00:55:20,883
I didn't want to see
his parents.

841
00:55:24,055 --> 00:55:27,206
You know, Kevin,

842
00:55:27,207 --> 00:55:30,358
